    • Uses of HeapPage in com.gridgraph.storage.heap.page

      Subclasses of HeapPage in com.gridgraph.storage.heap.page 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  EdgePrimaryHeapPage
      A EdgePrimaryHeapPage represents a fixed size block of binary data read from and written to file and cached as mapped memory for edge primary data.
      Data of an edge is stored separately: primary data means 'from/to vertex id', and 'next edge' for 'from/to vertex', while secondary data means 'previous edge id' for 'from/to vertex' and 'property tuple id'
      class  EdgePropertiesHeapPage
      A EdgePropertiesHeapPage represents a fixed size block of binary data read from and written to file and cached as mapped memory for edge properties data
      class  EdgeSecondaryHeapPage
      A EdgeSecondaryHeapPage represents a fixed size block of binary data read from and written to file and cached as mapped memory for edge secondary data.
      Data of an edge is stored separately: primary data means 'from/to vertex id', and 'next edge' for 'from/to vertex', while secondary data means 'previous edge id' for 'from/to vertex' and 'property tuple id'
      class  PropertiesHeapPage
      A PropertiesHeapPage represents a fixed size block of binary data read from and written to file and cached as mapped memory for element properties data
      class  VertexDegreeHeapPage
      A VertexDegreeHeapPage represents a fixed size block of binary data read from and written to file and cached as mapped memory for vertex degree data
      class  VertexPrimaryHeapPage
      A VertexPrimaryHeapPage represents a fixed size block of binary data read from and written to file and cached as mapped memory for vertex data
      Data of an vertex is stored separately: primary data means 'first edge id', and 'property id', while secondary data means 'in-degree' and 'out-degree'
      class  VertexPropertiesHeapPage
      A VertexPropertiesHeapPage represents a fixed size block of binary data read from and written to file and cached as mapped memory for vertex properties data
